        "localization": {
          "name": "Missile Storm",
          "description": "Consumes a Power Charge for 600% damage to all enemies. This attack ignores enemy damage reduction effects, Skin passive skills and the Counter Stance status effect. Each enemy hit is then randomly granted either the Deep Sleep status effect for 100TU (even if they have already slept while on the battlefield), or Frostburn. Usable only if the user has a Power Charge.\n\nDeep Sleep will overwrite other status effects, cannot be overwritten by Burn or Sleep status effects, and cannot be Purified. When a unit has Frostburn and they get the turn, they will lose the turn as if they were sleeping, then Frostburn is removed and that unit is granted the Burn status effect. Frostburn is not a status effect, but effects that remove negative status effects will also remove Frostburn. Frostburn will end if the affected unit is defeated or leaves the battlefield. Frostburn cannot apply to boss units, and cannot stack. Burn will overwrite other status effects. Any unit that deals damage to or is dealt damage by a unit with burn will also become burned.",
